    {
      "bookmarkId": "24181083_20_17610-17662",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "17610-17662",
      "markText": "十九年后杨立三去世，担任着国务院总理的周恩来，无论如何要亲自给他抬棺送葬。这是一种多么深挚的同志之情啊！",
      "totalCount": 684,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24181083&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=17610&rangeEnd=17662",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/af732df07170f95baf74fad?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=17610&rangeEnd=17662"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24181083_3_1650-1710",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1650-1710",
      "markText": "1924年11月，周恩来出任由国共两党合作创办的黄埔军校的政治部主任。他创建的行之有效的政治工作制度，使军校出现新面貌。",
      "totalCount": 663,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24181083&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1650&rangeEnd=1710",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/af732df07170f95baf74fad?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1650&rangeEnd=1710"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24181083_9_6710-6909",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6710-6909",
      "markText": "就在这一年（一九二一年）经张申府、刘清扬介绍，周恩来加入了中国共产党。从此，他把自己的全部精力和才能毫无保留地献给了共产主义事业，直到生命的最后一刻。",
      "totalCount": 656,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24181083&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6710&rangeEnd=6909",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/af732df07170f95baf74fad?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6710&rangeEnd=6909"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24181083_8_1540-1586",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1540-1586",
      "markText": "处于被统治状态的民众，以如此广泛的群众规模行动起来，直接干预政治，这在中国历史上还是第一次。",
      "totalCount": 608,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24181083&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1540&rangeEnd=1586",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/af732df07170f95baf74fad?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1540&rangeEnd=1586"
    },
    {
