      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "8482-8515",
      "markText": "他订了计划：每天读书十三小时半，休息和其他事三小时半，睡眠七小时。",
      "totalCount": 522,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24181083&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8482&rangeEnd=8515",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/af732df07170f95baf74fad?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8482&rangeEnd=8515"
    },
    {
